name: RTCRtpStreamStats.trackId
description: The RTCRtpStreamStats dictionary's trackId property is a string which uniquely identifies the RTCMediaStreamTrackStats object which contains the track statistics for the MediaStreamTrack for which statistics are provided in this object.
